.container
  #myCarousel.carousel.slide(data-ride="carousel")
    ol.carousel-indicators
      li.active(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='0')
      li(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='1')
      li(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide-to='2')
    .carousel-inner
        .item.active
            //img(src='data:image/png;base64,', data-src='#{pathToAssets}/assets/js/holder.js/100%x500/auto/#777:#7a7a7a/text:First slide', alt='First slide')
            .container
                .carousel-caption
                    h1 IndyVision
                    p
                        | Welcome to IndyVision! The most comprehensive and complete collection of things to do in Indianapolis.
                    p
                        a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='/signup') Sign up today
        .item
            //img(src='data:image/png;base64,', data-src='#{pathToAssets}/assets/js/holder.js/100%x500/auto/#777:#7a7a7a/text:Second slide', alt='Second slide')
            .container
                .carousel-caption
                    h1 Another example headline.
                    p
                        | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit.
                    p
                        a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='#') Learn more
        .item
            //img(src='data:image/png;base64,', data-src='#{pathToAssets}/assets/js/holder.js/100%x500/auto/#777:#7a7a7a/text:Third slide', alt='Third slide')
            .container
                .carousel-caption
                    h1 One more for good measure.
                    p
                        | Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Nullam id dolor id nibh ultricies vehicula ut id elit.
                    p
                        a.btn.btn-large.btn-primary(href='#') Browse gallery
    a.left.carousel-control(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide='prev')
        span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-left
    a.right.carousel-control(data-target='#myCarousel', data-slide='next')
        span.glyphicon.glyphicon-chevron-right

  .row
    .col-lg-12
        google-map(center="map.center", zoom="map.zoom", draggable="true")
  .row
    .col-md-6
      div(ng-include="'/partials/main/featured-events'")
    .col-md-6
      div(ng-include="'/partials/main/new-events'")